_sText:
I am employed as graphic designer in Sprint-trading advertising company. Head office is located in relatively small building, so I decided to rebuild it to CSS map. Results are stunning (on my opinion) - due to small area, map keeps good fps and proportions of rooms make map accessible and fun.

Dedicated to my colleagues from Sprint-trading company

THIS MAP CONTAINS BUGS! PLEASE DOWNLOAD UPDATED VERSION OF THIS MAP HERE 

This map or its parts is also used in my singleplayer mod

Have a fun
